title: Platinum Bundle Package
creator: Bobby Do-Good
description:
This is the PLATINUM BUNDLE package for the Bobby Do-Good LawnMower Service. The Platinum Bundle combines the most popular services from the Bronze, Silver, and Gold 
tiers into one premium, all-inclusive experience. Designed for homeowners who want a 
consistently flawless lawn without needing to manage scheduling or seasonal upkeep, this 
package delivers top-tier care all year long.  
This bundle includes:  
• Everything in the Gold Package  
• Monthly lawn health inspections  
• Seasonal weed control treatment  
• Soil pH testing and adjustment  
• Fall leaf removal service  
• Quarterly hedge and shrub sculpting  
• Premium customer hotline with 24-hr response  
• Discounted add-on services (aeration, reseeding, mulch upgrades, etc.)  
The Platinum Bundle is perfect for clients seeking maximum convenience, professional
grade maintenance, and the healthiest lawn on the block. If you're interested in this service, please email bobbydogoodbusiness@gmail.com to set up an appointment!
